    "comment": "# Voting NO on *Revised Cardano Summit 2026 Singapore*\n\n**May 20th 2026**\n\n## Summary\n\nThe Cardano Foundation is **again** asking for money to host the Cardano Summit. This time its a little bit less. \n\n## Conclusion\n\nNo. Its still not party time. I'm voting against this **again** for most of the same reasons as [last time](https://github.com/willpiam/drep/blob/master/vote_context/markdown/47_partytime.md). Please don't ask again. \n\n\nSigned, <br/>\nWilliam Doyle\n\nYour friendly neighbourhood DRep! <br/>\n$computerman <br/>\ndrep1yfpgzfymq6tt9c684e7vzata8r5pl4w84fmrjqeztdqw0sgpzw3nt <br/>\nhttps://x.com/william00000010 <br/>"
  },
